Example:

  script/generate event_calendar --model-name=bunny --view_name=rabbit

  This will create:
      
    # static files
      public/stylesheets/event_calendar.css
      public/javascripts/event_calendar.js
      
    # Unless --static-only option is given
      app/models/bunny.rb
      app/controllers/rabbit_controller.rb
      app/views/rabbit
      app/views/rabbit/index.html.erb
      app/helpers/rabbit_helper.rb
      db/migrate
      db/migrate/XXXX_create_bunnies.rb
      route match rabbit
